Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:49.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a misunderstanding with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:53.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:58.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\shad0\bord0.1\frz11\fscy95\be1\fs20\c&H171919&\3c&H262E35&\pos(688,93)}Yamada\NLiquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:00.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make my precious daughter cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:02.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do to my daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He just carried me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always jumping to conclusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:17.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-nine broken sake bottles...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:22.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Worth 38,000 yen in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your body hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:33.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The injuries from being thrown around by your dad aren't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then did you hit yourself somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:43.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My back and muscle pain from carrying you home is far worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say something like that to a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A 100 yen beef bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H535872&\shad0\bord0\fs22\frz2\pos(313,240)}Matsunoya {\c&HDBE7F2&}Inokashira Branch\N{\c&H535872&\fs18}100 Yen Beef Bowl (regular)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Matsunoya: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a pun on Yoshinoya, a popular beef bowl chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A beef bowl for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you like them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:10.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said that you'd be too embarrassed to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:12.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind then. I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:22.23,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama doesn't talk to me with a sad face anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you split your raw egg with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.56,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.07,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But also a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:36.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish my assignment, spring break will\Ncome, and I'll already be a third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you again next year, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:48.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't seem to feel like an upperclassman because\Nyou keep sticking around, Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:48.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't drink my drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already finished it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:04:00.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Finished! Finished! Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:02.72,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to keep fooling with me even when I'm a third year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Drank it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:06.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, this is Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:09.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,The endless torture and eternal pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, come over here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture is... from that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.64,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world that Hagu-chan sees?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.60,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is Shinobu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.60,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying ringtone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But that aside, "Shinobu-kun"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:06.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the big, tanned man with the\Nwhite beard who came to visit me last fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:13.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your former teacher and wrote the book that you really like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:22.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the Yamato would lose to the British fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:22.76,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Yamato: {\be1\3c&H000000&}flagship of Japan in WWII, one of the largest ships ever built.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We had Yamamoto Isoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Yamamoto Isoroku: {\be1\3c&H000000&}commander of the Japanese Navy during WWII.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:31.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make fun of King George V!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to think of you as a teacher anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:45.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two drank a lot of alcohol, talked about ships,\Nhad a huge fight, and were both crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't need to remember things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The man with the white beard is teaching\Nat a university in Kyoto now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he coming over again? Are you going to fight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to help him write a new book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:11.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to take about a year for the research and survey trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to travel back and forth between\NJapan, China, and Mongolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:21.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And during that time, I'll be teaching a class\Nwith that teacher at the university in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:25.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going, Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't responded yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come with me, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing no matter how many times I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:53.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,From hearing your stories, I agree that we\Nshouldn't leave Hagumi-chan behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:59.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if we do take her with us,\Nthe trip will be pretty tough on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:04.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see, I think that it'll also place\Na significant amount of stress on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the same goes for me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:18.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do get excited when I think about the pictures\Nshe'd draw if she saw foreign lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:32.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The change was gradual, so no one noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it might be that no one tried to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu! Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to middle school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the field day pretty soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:07:59.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:04.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Grandma will worry about me. I need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:13.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:18.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I always tell you to come straight home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As she got old and gradually lost her sight, my great-aunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:31.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...was no longer the strong and cheerful woman she once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:34.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, may I see your drawings again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They're on top of my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The yard during an evening shower, among the blooming azalea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:57.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The afternoon moon, the snowy sunset,\Nand the faraway thunderhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:05.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the vast amount of landscape paintings\Nwere all of the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:14.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them were quietly losing a place to go\Nto inside this large old house in a small village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:34.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come to my school\Nonce you graduate from high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:41.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of kids who draw pictures, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:46.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You might even find people you can get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:52.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you might be able to show your drawings\Nto each other or make something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:57.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I met someone there who I get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:02.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I wasn't very good at drawing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:09.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I became able to make a lot more things\Nthan when I used to draw by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:14.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was even able to find what I really wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:16.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right, Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:49.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just make things out of what you think and feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And will you take her with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that she collapsed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she's staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:22.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:28.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was probably surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:41.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the inside of my head became so white, it was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:49.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had decided to cherish Hagu as much as I possibly could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a part of me was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:58.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really a good idea to drag her out to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:07.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it actually help Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:08.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:12.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if I wasn't just being egoistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms are blooming again, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it remind you of the time we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a clumsy man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:36.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it stings my heart a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, where's Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. He's departing soon, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be busy getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, have you made requests for souvenirs yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A year will go by quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:22.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure that he'll come back to visit during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:24.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:39.05,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}aojiroki tamagawa ni omoi ukabete
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:39.05,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I let my thoughts drift over the pallid Tama River
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already working at Fujiwara Design Office, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Takaido-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:37.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're really working me hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:55.78,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}suberu you ni odayaka ni kyou ga kureteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:55.78,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The day peacefully slides away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:50.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:56.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:13.50,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kaze no tabibito ni akogareta kokoro yo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:13.50,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, the heart enthralled by the traveler of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:28.14,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}minamo no yosei wa tooi hibi no maboroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:28.14,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The water fairies are an illusion from the days long past
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:17.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:23.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I made it so that you can't take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll learn a lot of things and come back someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely come back, even if you won't be waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:42.03,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}boku no naka ni kimi no naka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:42.03,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're inside of me and inside of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please stay well until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:57.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Isn't he a silly boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:12.56,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kaze no tabibito ni akogareta kokoro yo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:12.56,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, the heart enthralled by the traveler of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:27.28,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}minamo no yosei wa tooi hibi no maboroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:27.28,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The water fairies are an illusion from the days long past
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:40.67,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}boku no naka ni kimi no naka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:40.67,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're inside of me and inside of you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:55.98,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}aojiroki tamagawa ni omoi ukabete
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:55.98,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I let my thoughts drift over the pallid Tama River
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it to Hanamoto-sensei's farewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to crawl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be getting together beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting at around 6 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already made the pouch for the good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now i just have to put the clover in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so that Shuu-chan can do his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:10.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so that Shuu-chan won't hurt himself or get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so that Shuu-chan's dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:22.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find the clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I told you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:41.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be living with Hagu-chan\Nwhile Hanamoto-sensei is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you won't be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:47.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:57.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Four-leaf clovers are usually around where people walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected of Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:08.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a wad of money inside my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:13.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... If you tap it, the wad of bills will become two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What are you doing? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Digging for treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:30.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama! You came at a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You help us look for it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? You're all covered in mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:18.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made too much food because you were so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:23.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're all hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:31.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Sensei... Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan wanted to give you a good luck charm—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:40.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You see... there wasn't... a four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should I do? I couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anything like it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:59.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone helped me look for it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:09.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so that Shuu-chan's dream would come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:12.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so that you wouldn't hurt yourself or get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something like "I couldn't find it."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already given me so much, Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:37.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we all washed our hands and\Nsat in front of the steaming pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:45.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As I looked across the table at everyone's faces, I dreamily\Nremembered the blue sky that I saw from the riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:52.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The day will surely come when everything\Nends and turns into a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that I'll reminisce about it again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:07.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we searched for that one thing, under the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:13.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the scent of the wind permeating through the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:18.86,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:18.86,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.99,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.99,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:33.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Unable to leave you alone.
